platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: If you ever see a group of teenagers (or twenty- or thirtysomethings) filming themselves doing literally anything, know this: They’re probably making a video to share on TikTok. Its infinite scroll of new videos combines perfectly edited lip-synching, hilarious sketches, and mesmerizing dance moves with delightful special effects and filters. It’s hard not to fall in love with everyone’s fluffy pets, awkward parents, impressive glow-ups, fails of every kind, and songs and pop-culture references that spark a million memes.

If you see people filming themselves doing literally anything, they’re probably doing it for this. Scroll infinitely through perfect lip-syncs and dance moves, hilarious sketches, fluffy pets, and bites of pop culture that spark a million memes.

Si vous voyez des gens se filmer en train de faire n’importe quoi, c’est sûrement pour cette app ! Scrollez entre une infinité de playbacks, de chorégraphies, de sketchs hilarants, d’animaux tout doux et de fragments de culture pop qui ont donné naissance aux meilleurs mèmes.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Make awesome short music videos that you can share with the world.
Créez des vidéos géniales à partager avec le monde entier.
